OL,3,C'We should have acted faster on Letby'
OL,4,Csays new head of nursing watchdog
OL,6,FMr Rees said: "We have to be honest
OL,7,Fabout things that have gone wrong. And
OL,8,Fthings have gone wrong in the past."
OL,10,FThe Independent reported that the NMC
OL,11,Fhas not investigated nurses accused of
OL,12,Fabuse, sexual assault and domestic
OL,13,Fviolence outside the workplace, as it
OL,14,Fdid not consider this to be in its
OL,15,Fremit.
