OL,3,C'We should have acted faster on Letby'
OL,4,Csays new head of nursing watchdog
OL,6,FMr Rees said: "The issue was that the
OL,7,Fguidance stated where nursing and
OL,8,Fmidwifery or professionals did
OL,9,Fsomething outside of their working
OL,10,Flife, it was outside of our concerns `
OL,11,Fthat was completely wrong.
OL,13,F"It should've been saying what you do
OL,14,Foutside of work is just as important
OL,15,Fas what you do at work."
OL,17,FLady Thirwall's final report on the
OL,18,Fpublic inquiry into authorities'
OL,19,Fhandling of the Letby case is due next
OL,20,Fyear.
