OL,3,C'We should have acted faster on Letby'
OL,4,Csays new head of nursing watchdog
OL,6,FAsked if he expects it to criticise
OL,7,Fthe regulator, Mr Rees said: "We don't
OL,8,Fknow yet, but it's a possibility
OL,9,Fbecause we should've acted faster with
OL,10,FLucy Letby.
OL,12,F"We've changed the guidance, so it is
OL,13,Fclear now where there is an
OL,14,Fexceptional case of serious criminal
OL,15,Fwrongdoing, we take action and
OL,16,Fimplement an interim order. It's
OL,17,Fincumbent upon us to move fast and
OL,18,Fbring about these interim orders."
