OL,3,C'We should have acted faster on Letby'
OL,4,Csays new head of nursing watchdog
OL,6,FThe NMC was contacted by the Countess
OL,7,Fof Chester Hospital's then director of
OL,8,Fnursing Alison Kelly in July 2016,
OL,9,Fafter consultant paediatricians raised
OL,10,Ffears to executives that Letby may be
OL,11,Fdeliberately harming babies on the
OL,12,Fneonatal unit.
OL,14,FShe was redeployed to non-clinical
OL,15,Fduties, but was due to return to the
OL,16,Fneonatal unit before the move was put
OL,17,Fon hold as hospital chiefs finally
OL,18,Fcontacted Cheshire Constabulary in May
OL,19,F2017 to ask them to investigate the
OL,20,Fincreased number of deaths.
