OL,3,C'We should have acted faster on Letby'
OL,4,Csays new head of nursing watchdog
OL,6,FLetby, 35, was given 14 whole life
OL,7,Forders in August 2023 after being
OL,8,Ffound guilty at Manchester Crown Court
OL,9,Fof the seven murders and six attempted
OL,10,Fmurders.
OL,12,FShe was given a further whole life
OL,13,Forder in July 2024 after being
OL,14,Fconvicted of attempting to murder
OL,15,Fanother baby.
